title: Still not seeded after provisionals
body:
The title says it all. I went 7-3 in my provisionals, but I'm still not seeded/placed into any league.

Im fairly new to ranked, and might just not understand provisionals. Any advice/help is appreciated.

replies.body: you do realise your account is NA? lolking says you are gold 4 anyway
Lolking says Im still not seeded. Infact, it says that I've only 9 games. But in "ranked matches" these are clearly 10 games played.

> [{quoted}](name=xgenoriginal,realm=OCE,application-id=Ntey9fRZ,discussion-id=mv8y8NEn,comment-id=0001,timestamp=2015-02-03T07:49:00.116+0000)
>
> you do realise your account is NA? lolking says you are gold 4 anyway

A couple of people said they couldn't get on the OCE forums with their OCE account for whatever reason this morning.

Usually pops up at the post-game lobby screen after your 10th game.

Just play again, see what happens.
